\paragraph{C.71: incentive constraint and capital demand.}
The source level condition behind C.71 is
\begin{align}
\nu_{n,t}N_t+(\lambda_L+\nu_{L,t})L^q_t
&=(\lambda_{k,t}-\nu_{k,t})Q_tK_{b,t}
\nonumber\\
&\quad
+(\lambda_b-\nu_{b,t})Q^b_tB_{b,t}.
\label{eq:bgs-c71-level-repeat}
\end{align}
