\nonumber\\
&\quad
+(\lambda_k-\nu_k)K_b(q_t+k_{b,t}),
\label{eq:bgs-c71-left-expansion}
\end{align}
where $Q=1$ under the local price normalization. In the source's hat
notation, this is written as
\[
